Intro
 
SIMPLE & SECURE Learn More


 VerifyMe ™ is a pioneer in combining patented physical, cyber and biometric security solutions to prevent identity theft, counterfeiting and fraud. 












































Digital Solutions
 
FORGET YOUR PASSWORDSVerifyMe™ ID services replaces passwords, PINs and 2-factor solutions with intuitive, user-friendly, multi-factor authentication, incorporating biometrics, to protect consumer and corporate integrity. Learn About Digital Tech






Digital Solutions
 
FORGET YOUR PASSWORDSVerifyMe™ ID services replaces passwords, PINs and 2-factor solutions with intuitive, user-friendly, multi-factor authentication, incorporating biometrics, to protect consumer and corporate integrity. Learn About Digital Tech












Physical Solutions
 
STATE-OF-THE-ART SECURITYVerifyMe offers a comprehensive platform for identifying and protecting products and consumers.  We offer innovative custom-designed brand authentication solutions and anti-counterfeiting services that can protect your brand and customers against fraud, diversion and tampering. Learn About Physical Tech






Physical Solutions
 
STATE-OF-THE-ART SECURITYVerifyMe offers a comprehensive platform for identifying and protecting products and consumers.  We offer innovative custom-designed brand authentication solutions and anti-counterfeiting services that can protect your brand and customers against fraud, diversion and tampering. Learn About Physical Tech








