VerifyMe, Inc. Key Developments

VerifyMe, Inc. Announces Board Appointments
Jul 20 17
On July 14, 2017, VerifyMe, Inc. elected as members of the board of directors Howard Goldberg, Paul Klapper, Laurence J. Blickman, Marshall S. Geller, and Patrick White, to serve as directors of the company. Mr. Goldberg was appointed to the Executive Committee of the company. Mr. White presently serves as a consultant to the company.


VerifyMe, Inc. Announces Resignation of Jonathan Weinberger from Board of Directors
Apr 26 17
On April 20, 2017, Jonathan Weinberger informed the board of directors of VerifyMe, Inc. of his resignation, effective immediately, from the company’s board of directors and all of its committees due to the time and resource requirements of Mr. Weinberger’s new professional obligations.


VerifyMe, Inc. announced delayed annual 10-K filing
Apr 3 17
On 04/03/2017, VerifyMe, Inc. announced that they will be unable to file their next 10-K by the deadline required by the SEC.


